headline: Analog Devices: Don't Jump On Conclusions From Recent Earnings (Rating Upgrade)
summary: Analog Devices beat Q2 estimates, but expectations tempered the stock move; growth drivers and valuation look compelling. See why ADI stock is upgraded to buy.
